hadiths[210]{hadithnumber,text}:
4304,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dhaari daar kapda zeb tan karna ziyada pasand kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
4305,Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tang aastinon wala Rumi jubba zebtan kya. muttafaq aleh.
4306,"Hazrat abu-Burda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne pewand lagi hui eik chadar aur eik moti tehband hamen dikhai aur farmaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki un do kapdon mein rooh qabz ki gaee. muttafaq aleh."
4307,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jis bistar par aaram farmaya kartey they, wo chamdey ka tha jis mein khajoor ke pattey bharey huey they. muttafaq aleh."
4308,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka takiya jis par aap tek lagaya kartey they wo chamdey ka tha jis mein khajoor ke pattey bharey huey they. rawahu Muslim ."
4309,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, ham dopehar ki garmi mein apney ghar mein bethey huey they ke kisi ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ye chadar ke kinarey se sar dhanp kar tashrif laney waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. Bukhari ."
4310,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''eik bistar aadmi ke liye, eik uski ehliya ke liye, teesra mehman ke liye aur chotha (agar ho to wo) shetan ke liye hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4311,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah roze-qiyamat us shakhs ki taraf ( nazar rehmat sey) nahin dekhega jo takabbur ke taur par apna izaar ghaseet-ta hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
4312,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah roze-qiyamat us shakhs ki taraf ( rehmat ki nazar sey) nahin dekhega jo takabbur ke taur par apna kapda ghaseet-ta hai.'' muttafaq aleh.
4313,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' is beech mein ke eik aadmi takabbur ke taur par apna tehband ghaseet-taa tha, us wajeh se usey zamin mein dhansa diya gaya, aur wo roze-qiyamat tak zamin mein dhansta chala jaeyga.'' Bukhari ."
4314,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tehband jo takhnon se nichey ho jaey jahannam mein) ley jata ( hai.'' Bukhari ."
4315,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi apney baaeyn haath se khaye ya eik joota pehan kar chaley aur ye ke wo apney purey jism par is tarah chadar lapet ley ke haath bhi na nikal saken, aur ye ke wo eik kapda is tarah lapet ley ke sharm-gah nangi ho.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4316,"Hazrat Umar, Anas, ibne-Zubair aur abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein resham pahnta hai wo usey aakhirat mein nahin pehnega.'' muttafaq aleh."
4317,"Hazrat umr , Anas , ibne-Zubair aur Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein resham pahntaa hai wo usey aakhirat mein nahin pehneyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4318,"Hazrat umr , Anas , ibne-Zubair aur abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein resham pahnta hai wo usey aakhirat mein nahin pehnega .'' muttafaq aleh."
4319,"Hazrat umr , Anas , ibne-Zubair aur abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein resham pahnta hai wo usey aakhirat mein nahin pehnega .'' muttafaq aleh."
4320,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''duniya mein sirf wohi shakhs resham pahntaa hai jiska aakhirat mein koi hissey nahin .'' muttafaq aleh."
4321,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne soney chaandi ke bartan mein khaney-peeney, resham aur deebaaj ( resham ki eik qism ( pehanney aur is par bethney se hamen mana farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4322,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko reshmi jodey ka tohfa pesh kya gaya to aapney usey meri taraf bhej diya, maine wo pehan liya, lekin) baad mein) maine aap ke chehrey par narazi dekhi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine usey tumhari taraf isliye nahin bheja tha ke tum usey pehan lo, maine to usey tumhari taraf isliye bheja tha ke tum usey phaad kar khawatin ki odhniyan bana lo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4323,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne resham pehanney se mana farmaya, magar do ungliyon ki miqdaar ke barabar ijazat farmaey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni darmiyani aur shahadat ki ungli ko mila kar unhen buland karkey us miqdaar ki wazahat farmaai. muttafaq aleh."
4324,aur Muslim mein hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (shaam ke shehar) jaabiya ke maqam par khitab kartey huey farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do ya teen ya chaar ungliyon ke jitna resham pehanney ki ijazat di hai. rawahu Muslim.
4325,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Tiyalisi kasarowaani jubba nikala jiskey gireban aur dono chaakon par deebaaj (resham) ka tukdaa laga hua tha, unhoney farmaya : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka jubba tha jo ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey zeb tan farmaya kartey they, ham marizon ke liye usey dhotey hain aur uskey (pani ke) sath shifa hasil kartey hain. rawahu Muslim."
4326,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Zuber aur Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaarish ki wajeh se resham pehanney ki rukhsat inayat farmaai thi. aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unhoney juon ki shikayat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen reshmi qamis pehanney ki ijazat inayat farmaey. muttafaq aleh."
4327,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey zard rang ke do kapdey pehney huey dekha to farmaya : ''ye kuffar ke kapdon mein se hain, tum unhen mat pehna karo.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai, maine arz kya, main unhen dho dalun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, balke unhen jala dalo.'' rawahu Muslim. aur ham Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ''eik roz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye . . . . .''baab manaaqib ehle-bait Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein zikr karengey."
4328,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko libas mein qamis sabse ziyada pasand thi. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
4329,"Hazrat Asma bint Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qamis ke aasteen kalaai aur haath ke darmiyaney jod tak they. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4330,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qamis zebtan farmatey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aaghaz daain taraf se farmatey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4331,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna : ''momin ka izaar uski nisf pindli tak hona chahiye, aur agar wo nisf pindli aur takhnon ke darmiyan ho to bhi is par koi gunah nahin, aur jo us se nichey ho to wo aag mein (ley jata) hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye teen baar farmaya .''Allah roze-qiyamat us shakhs ki taraf (nazar rehmat sey) nahin dekhega jo takabbur ke taur par apna izaar ghaseet-ta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w ibne-Maja ."
4332,"Hazrat Salim apney walid sey, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kapdey ka latkana tehband, qamis aur amaamey mein hai. jo shakhs un mein se kuch bhi az-raahe-takabbur latkaata hai to Allah roze-qiyamat uski taraf (nazare-rehmat sey) nahin dekhega.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
4333,"Hazrat abu Kabsha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba ki topiyan saron ke sath lagi huin thin (yani ooper uthi hui nahin thin). Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees munkar hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4334,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne izaar ka tazkira farmaya to unhoney us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aurat ke liye tehband mein kya hukm hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo eik baalisht nichey latkaaey .'' unhoney arz kya : tab to uskey paaon nangey honey ka imkan hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' eik haath , aur us se ziyada nahin .'' rawahu Malik w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
4335,"Tirmizi aur Nasai ki ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya : tab to unke paaon nazar aaeyngey, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo eik haath (izaar) latka lein aur us se ziyada nahin. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
4336,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main muzena qabeele ke eik qafley ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , unhoney aap ki baiat ki, dar-aan-haaleke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke batan khuley huey they, maine aapki qamis ke gireban mein apna haath dakhil kya to maine mohare-nabuwat ko chhua. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4337,Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safed libas pehna karo kyonkey wo ziyada pakizah aur ziyada paak hai aur apney mardon ko usi mein kafnao.'' rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai w ibne-Maja .
4338,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) amaama baandhtey to apney amaamey ka shamla apney kandhon ke darmiyan latka letey. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4339,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey sar par dastaar baandhi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey eik kinarey ko aagey ki taraf aur doosrey kinarey ko peechey ki taraf latka diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4340,"Hazrat Rukana (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamarey aur mushrekin ke darmiyan jo farq hai wo topiyon par amaamey baandhna hai.'' Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai aur uski asnaad durust nahin. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4341,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sona aur resham meri ummat ki khawatin ke liye halal kya gaya hai aur uskey mardon par haram kya gaya hai.'' Tirmizi, Nasai , aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
4342,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) naya kapda pahanten to uska naam letey maslan amama , ya qamis ya chadar , phir farmatey : ''aey Allah ! terey liye hamd hai jaisa ke to ne mujhey ye pehnaya, main tujh se uski achchhai ka aur jis khair aur barkat ke liye isey banaya gaya hai, uska sawal karta hun. aur main iskey shar se aur jis ke liye ye banaya gaya hai, us se teri panah chahta hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood."
4343,Hazrat Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs khana kha kar ye dua padhta hai : ''her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey ye khana khilaya aur merey tasarruf aur quwat ke baghair isey mujhey ata farmaya.'' uskey sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' aur Abu-Dawood ne ye izafa naqal kiya hai : ''jo shakhs libas pehan kar ye dua padhta hai : ''her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey ye pehnaya aur merey tasarruf aur quwat ke baghair isey mujhey ata farmaya.'' to us shakhs ke sabiqa gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood.
4344,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''Aaisha ! agar tum mera sath chahti ho to phir tumhen sawar ke zaade-raah jitni duniya kafi honi chahiye. tum maal daaron ki ham nasheenon se bacho , aur kisi kapdey ko puraanaa aur boseedah mat khayal karo yahan tak ke tum usey pewand na laga lo.'' isey Imam Tirmizi ne riwayat kiya hai aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ham isey Saleh bin Hassan ki hadees ke hawaley se jantey hain. aur Muhammad bin Ismail (Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : Saleh bin Hassan munkire-hadees hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4345,"Hazrat Abu-Umama Ayas bin Solba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''suno ! suno ! saada libas eman ka hissa hai, saada libas eman ka hissa hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4346,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs duniya mein shohrat wala libas pahntaa hai to Allah Taala usey roze-qiyamat zillat wala libas pahnaaeyga.'' rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood aur ibne-Maja."
4347,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi qom se mushaabihat ikhtiyar karta hai wo unhi mein se hai.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4348,"Hazrat Suwed bin Wahab, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab ki aulad mein se kisi aadmi se riwayat kartey hain, wo aadmi apney walid sey, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne taqat ke bawajud aur eik riwayat ke mutabiq tawaazeh mehman-nawazi ke taur par khoobsurat libas pehan-na tarak kar diya, Allah usey izzat aur karaamat ka joda pahnaaeyga, aur jis shakhs ne Allah ki raza ki khatir (apney martabe aur meyaar se kam martaba aurat sey) shaadi ki to Allah usey badshahat ka taaj pahnaaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4349,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi ne un se Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki sanad se hadees libas riwayat ki hai. rawahu Tirmizi.
4350,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah pasand farmata hai ke us bandey par uski nemat ka asar dikhai dey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ."
4351,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan mulaqat ke liye tashrif laye to aapney eik bikhrey baalon wala shakhs dekha aur farmaya : ''kya ye shakhs aisi koi chiz nahin paata jiskey sath wo apney sar ke baal durust kar leta?'' aur aapney eik shakhs ko mailey kapdey pehney huey dekha to farmaya : ''kya ye shakhs aisi koi chiz nahin paata jiskey zariey wo apna libas dho leta?'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai ."
4352,"Hazrat abul-Ahwas apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua maine ghair maiyaari kapdey pehney huey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''kya tumharey paas maal hai? ''maine arz kya : ji haan! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maal ki kon si qism tumharey paas hai? ''maine arz kya : oont, gaey, bakri , ghodey aur ghulam her qism ka maal Allah Taala ne mujhey ata kar rakha hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne tumhen maal dey rakha hai to phir Allah ki nemat aur uski izzat w karaamat ka asar tum par zahir hona chahiye.'' usey Ahmed aur Nasai ne riwayat kya hai aur Sharahus-sunnah mein masaabeh ke alfaz hain. ( rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4353,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi guzra usney surkh joda pehna hua tha, usney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kya to aapney uskey salam ka jawab na diya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4354,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main surkh zeen posh par Sawar hota hun na kusum mein ranga hua kapda pahnta hun aur na hi mein aisi qamis pahnta hun jis par resham laga hua ho.'' aur farmaya : '' sun lo ! mardon ki khushbu wo hai jis mein mehak ho magar rang numaya na ho. jabkey khawatin ki khushbu wo hai jis mein mehak na ho aur rang ho.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood.
4355,"Hazrat abu-Rehana (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne das ( khaslaton ( se mana farmaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daant bareek karney, sui ke sath jism godney, (chehrey ya palkon waghera sey) baal ukhaadney, mard ka mard ke sath aur aurat ka aurat ke sath eik hi chadar ( odhni) mein ham khuwab honey sey, ye ke aadmi ajmiyon ki tarah apney kapdon ke nichey resham lagaey, ya wo apney kandhon par ajmiyon ki tarah resham lagaey, loot-maar karney sey, chheetey ki khaal ( ki zeen ( par sawari karney se aur sahibe-iqtidar shakhs ke siwa anguthi pehanney se mana farmaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4356,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey soney ki anguthi pehanney aur qas ka resham pehanney aur zeen posh se mana farmaya. Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, Nasai , ibne-Maja . aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne surkh zeen posh se mana farmaya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
4357,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum reshmi zeen posh par Sawar ho na chheetey ki khaal par.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ( ."
4358,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne surkh zeen posh se mana farmaya hai. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( .
4359,"Hazrat abu-Ramsa Taimi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , aapney sabz (hara) joda zeb tan kya hua tha, aur aap ke chand baalon par budhapa numaya tha aur aap ke safed baal mehndi laganey ki wajeh se surkh they. Tirmizi . aur Abu-Dawood ki riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zulfein kanon ki lo tak thin aur un par mehndi ka asar tha. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood ."
4360,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mareez they, aap Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ka sahara liye bahar tashrif laye, aap par Qatar ki) yamnii ( chadar thi jis ko aapney jism par lapeta hua tha, phir aapney unhen Namaz padhaai. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4361,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par do yamni motey kapdey they, jab aap (der tak) bethtey to aap ko paseena aa jata aur wo kapdey aap par bhari ho jatey , falan Yahudi ka mulk Sham se kapda aaya to maine arz kya : agar aap uskey paas kisi aadmi ko bhej kar khushhali ke wadey tak us se do kapdey kharid lein (to behtar hai), aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski taraf aadmi bheja to usney kaha : mujhey pata hai ke tum kya chahtey ho, tum to mera maal hathiyaana chahtey ho, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''wo jhoota hai, halanke usey pata hai ke main un sab se ziyada muttaqi aur un sab se ziyada bar waqt adaegi karney wala hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
4362,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dekha, mujh par gulaabi kusum ka ranga hua kapda tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye kya hai? ''maine aap ki nagawari ko jaan liya aur maine ja kar us ( kapdey ( ko jala diya, uskey baad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne apney kapdey ka kya kya ?'' maine arz kya, maine usey jala diya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne usey apney ehle-khana mein se kisi ko kyon na pehna diya? kyonkey usey aurton ke pehanney mein koi muzaaeqa nahin .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4363,"Hazrat Hilal bin Aamir apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khachar par Sawar ho kar Mina mein khitab kartey huey dekha us waqt aap par surkh chadar thi jabkey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) , aap ke aagey they aur wo aap ki baat aagey logon tak pahuncha rahey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4364,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye kaali chadar tayyar ki gaee to aapney usey pehan liya, jab aap ko is mein paseena aaya aur aapney oon ki bu mehsus ki to aapney usey utaar diya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4365,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap eik chadar mein got maar kar bethey huey they, aur uskey phundney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qadmon par they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4366,"Hazrat Dahiya bin khalifa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein qibt ( Misr (ke baney huey safed bareek kapdey pesh kiye gaey to aapney un mein se eik kapda mujhey inayat kya aur farmaya : ''uskey do tukdey kar lena, un mein se eik se qamis bana lena aur doosra apni ehliya ko dey dena jiski wo odhni bana ley.'' jab wo wapis mudey to farmaya : ''apni ehliya ko kehna ke uskey nichey eik aur kapda laga ley taake uskey jism ka pata na chaley.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4367,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif laye to wo odhni odh rahi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik pher do, do ki zarurat nahin.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4368,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra is haal mein ke mera tehband latak raha tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( dekh kar) farmaya : '' Abdullah ! apna tehband ooncha karo.'' maine ooncha kar liya . phir farmaya : '' mazeed ooncha karo.'' maine mazeed ooncha kar liya , main uskey baad uska bahut khayal rakhta raha , logon mein se kisi ne puchha : ( tehband ( kahan tak ? unhoney farmaya : nisf pindliyon tak . rawahu Muslim ."
4369,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs takabbur ke taur par apna kapda ghaseet'ta hai to roze-qiyamat Allah uski taraf (nazare-rehmat sey) nahin dekhega.'' (ye sun kar) abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! merey khayal rakhney ke bawajud mera tehband latak jata hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen farmaya : '' aap un mein se nahin jo takabbur ke taur par aisa kartey hain.'' Bukhari .
4370,"Hazrat Ikrima bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke wo tehband baandhtey to agli janib se tehband ka kinara apney paaon ki pusht par rakhtey aur pichli janib se usey utha kar rakhtey they, maine kaha : aap is tarah kyon tehband baandhtey hain? unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah tehband baandhtey huey dekha hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4371,"Hazrat Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' pagadiyaan baandha karo, kyonkey wo farishton ki alamat hain, aur unka shamla apni pusht ke peechey chhoda karo.'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( ."
4372,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bareek kapdey pehney huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ayen to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se rukh mod liya aur farmaya : '' Asma ! jab aurat baligh ho jaey to uskey jism ka koi hissey siwaye is, iskey dekhna durust nahin.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney chehrey aur haathon ki taraf ishara kya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4373,"Hazrat Abu-Matr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne teen dirham main eik kapda kharida, jab unhoney usey pehna to yun kaha : her qism ki tareef Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey libas ata kya jiskey zariey main logon mein khoobsurti hasil karta hun, aur uskey zariey apna sattar dhaanpta hun, phir unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko isi tarah farmatey huey suna hai. rawahu Ahmed ."
4374,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne naya kapda pehna to ye dua ki : her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey libas pehnaya jiskey zariey mein apna sattar dhaanpta hun aur uskey zariey main apni zindagi mein khoobsurti hasil karta hun, phir unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs naya kapda pehan kar ye dua padhta hai : '' her qism ki hamd Allah ke liye hai jisney mujhey libas pehnaya , jiskey zariey mein apna sattar dhaanpta hun aur uskey zariey main apni zindagi mein khoobsurti hasil karta hun.'' phir wo shakhs us kapdey ka qasd (irada) karey jo usney puraana kar diya aur wo usey sadqa kar dey to wo shakhs duniya aur aakhirat mein Allah ki hifz w aman aur uski panah mein hota hai.'' Ahmed, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja ."
4375,"Hazrat Alqama bin abi Alqama apni walida se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : Hafsa bint Abdur-Rehman, Aaisha ke paas ayen to un par bareek chadar thi, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne usey phaad diya, aur unhen moti chadar pehna di. rawahu Malik."
4376,"Hazrat Abdul Wahid bin Aiman apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to unhoney paanch dirham ki Qatri qamis zeb tan kar rakhi thi, unhoney farmaya : meri londi ki taraf nazar uthao aur usey dekho, kyonkey wo ghar mein bhi aisa kapda pehanna pasand nahin karti , jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ehad mein bhi merey paas isi tarah ki eik qamis thi, Madina mein jis bhi aurat ka ( shaadi ke moqe par) banaao singaar kya jata to wo usey mustaar leney ke liye meri taraf pegham bhejti thi. Bukhari ."
4377,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik roz reshmi quba pahni jo ke aap ko hadiya ki gaee thi, phir aapney jaldi se utara aur usey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bhej diya, arz kya gaya : Allah ke Rasool ! aapney usey utaarney mein bahut jaldi ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne mujhey us se rok diya.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) rotey huey aaye aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! eik chiz ko aapney napasand farmaya aur wo chiz mujhey de-di, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine tumhen isliye nahin di ke tum usey pehen lo, balke maine to wo tumhen isliye di ke tum usey bech do.'' unhoney wo do hazar dirham mein bech di. rawahu Muslim."
4378,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sirf us kapdey se mana farmaya hai jo khalis reshmi ho, raha reshmi kinara ya wo kapda jiska taana reshmi ho to uskey pehanney mein koi muzaaeqa nahinx. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4379,"Hazrat abu-Rija bayan kartey hain, Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas tashrif laye, un par chadar thi jis ka kinara Khaz ( resham aur oon se bana hua ( tha aur unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah jis shakhs ko koi nemat se nawazey to Allah pasand karta hai ke uski nemat uskey bandey par zahir ho.'' rawahu Ahmed ."
4380,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : israaf aur badai se ijtinab kartey huey jo chaho so khaao aur jo chaho so pahno. Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey ( ترجمۃ الباب ( mein riwayat kya hai. ( Bukhari ( .
4381,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se bayan kartey hain, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khaao piyo , sadqa karo aur pehno, lekin israaf aur badai se ijtinab karo.'' rawahu Ahmed w Nasai w ibne-Maja ."
4382,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' behtareen libas jis main tumhen apni qabron aur apni masaajid mein Allah se mulaqat kerni chahiye wo safed libas hai.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ."
4383,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi hasil ki, eik dusri riwayat mein hai : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey daain haath mein pehna , phir usey phenk diya, phir aapney chaandi ki anguthi hasil ki jis par Muhammad Rasulullah naqsh kya gaya tha, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi shakhs meri us anguthi ke naqsh ki tarah kanda na karey.'' aur jab aap usey pehantey to uskey nageeney ko hatheli ki andruni taraf kar letey. muttafaq aleh."
4384,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qas ke aur zard rang ke kapdey pehenney, soney ki anguthi pehenney aur rukoo mein Quran padhney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Muslim."
4385,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisi aadmi ke haath mein soney ki anguthi dekhi to usey utaar kar phenk diya, aur farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs aag ke angaarey ka qasd (irada) karta hai to usey apney haath par rakh leta hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tashrif ley janey ke baad us aadmi se kaha gaya, apni anguthi pakad lo aur us se faeyda uthao, usney kaha : Allah ki qasam! jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey phenk diya hai to main usey kabhi bhi nahin uthaunga. rawahu Muslim ."
4386,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kisra, qaisar aur Najashi ke naam khat likhney ka irada farmaya to aap se arz kya gaya ke wo sirf sr-b-muhr khat hi wasul kartey hain, tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaandi ke halqey ki anguthi banwaai, is mein '' Muhammad Rasulullah '' naqsh kya gaya. Muslim aur Bukhari ki riwayat mein hai : anguthi ka naqsh teen linon mein tha : ''Muhammad'' eik line mein'', Rasool '' eik line mein aur ''Allah '' eik line mein tha. muttafaq aleh."
4387,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi chaandi ki thi, aur uska nageena bhi usi ka tha. Bukhari ."
4388,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne chaandi ki anguthi apney daain haath mein pahni, is mein Habshi nageena tha, aap uska nageena apni hatheli ki taraf rakhtey they. muttafaq aleh."
4389,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki anguthi us (ungli) mein thi, aur unhoney baaein hath ki chhanguli ki taraf ishara kya. rawahu Muslim ."
4390,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey mana farmaya ke main apni us ya us ungli mein anguthi pahnun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darmiyani aur uskey sath wali (shahadat ki ungli) ki taraf ishara kya. rawahu Muslim ."
4391,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney daain haath mein anguthi pehna kartey they. rawahu ibne-Maja."
4392,Hazrat Imam Abu-Dawood aur Imam Nasai ne usey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai.
4393,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney baaeyn haath mein anguthi pehna kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4394,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne resham pakda aur usey apney daain haath par rakh liya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sona pakda aur usey apney baaein hath par rakh liya, phir farmaya : ''be-shak ye dono chizen meri ummat ke mardon par haram hain.'' rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
4395,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne cheeton ki khaal par sawari karney aur sona pehanney se mana farmaya, haan albatta tukdon ki shakal mein pehanney ki rukhsat farmaai. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4396,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko peetal ki anguthi pehney huey dekha to usey farmaya : ''mujhey kya hai ke main tujh se buton ki bu mehsus kar raha hun?'' us shakhs ne usey phenk diya. phir wo aaya to usney lohey ki anguthi pehan rakhi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey kya hai ke main tujh par jahannamiyon ka zewar dekh raha hun?'' usney usey phenk diya, aur arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! main kis dhaat se anguthi banwaaun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''chaandi se aur wo bhi misqal se kam ho.'' aur Muhiussunna (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : haq mehar ke barey mein Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) se sahih sanad ke sath Sabit hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi se farmaya : '' talash karo chahey lohey ki eik anguthi ho.'' ( rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai w fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4397,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) das baaten napasand farmatey they. Zaafran lagana, budhapey ko (kaalaa khizaab laga kar) tabdili karna, tehband ghaseet-taa, soney ki anguthi pehenna, moqey mehal ke baghair banaao-singaar zahir karna, shatranj khelna, muawwizaat ke ilawa kisi aur wird se dam karna, mankey baandhna, pani (yani mani) ka uski asal jagah ( sharm-gah (ke baghair khaarij karna aur bachey ke doodh ko kharab karna (yani doodh pilaney ki muddat mein aurat se jima karna) lekin usey haram qarar nahin diya gaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4398,"Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unki eik azad karda londi thi wo Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti ko, jiskey paaon mein ghunghruon they, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ley gaee, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhen kaat dala aur farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' her ghanti (ghoongroo) ke sath shetan hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4399,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Hayyan Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki azad karda londi banaana, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas mojud thi, achcha koi bachi unke paas laee gaee usney ghunghroo pehan rakhey they jinse aawaz aa rahi thi, Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : usey merey paas us waqt tak mat aaney dena jab tak tum uskey ghunghroo nahin kaat detey kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis ghar mein ghanti ho us mein) rehmat ke) farishtey dakhil nahin hotey .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4400,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Tarfa se riwayat hai ke kilaab ki ladaai ke din unke dada Arfaja bin Asad (Raziallahu anhu) ki naak kaat di gaee to unhoney chaandi ki naak laga li, wo badbudaar ho gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey soney ki naak laganey ka hukm diya. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4401,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney dost ko aag ka chhalla pahanana pasand karta hai to wo usey soney ka chhalla pehna dey , jo shakhs apney dost ko aag ka toq pahanaana pasand karta hai to wo usey soney ka toq pehna dey , jo shakhs apney dost ko aag ke kangan pahanaana pasand karta hai to wo usey soney ke kangan pehna dey , lekin tum chaandi ko lazim pakdo aur uskey zewar banaao.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4402,"Hazrat Asma binte-Yazid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ne soney ka haar pehna to roze-qiyamat uski gardan mein aag ka haar dala jaeyga, aur jis aurat ne apney kaan mein soney ki baali pehni to Allah roze-qiyamat uskey kaan mein usi ki misl aag dal dega .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4403,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki behan se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khawatin ki jamaat ! tumhen kya hai ke tum chaandi ka zewar nahin banati ho, tum mein se jo aurat soney ka zewar banati hai aur usey zahir karti hai to usey uski wajeh se azab diya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4404,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) zewrat aur resham pehenney walon ko mana kya kartey they aur farmaya kartey they : ''agar tum jannat ka zewar aur uska resham pasand kartey ho to tum usey duniya mein mat pahno .'' rawahu Nasai .
4405,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne anguthi banwaai aur usey pehan liya , ( phir ( farmaya : '' usney aaj mujhey tum se mashghool kar diya, main eik nazar uski taraf aur eik nazar tumhari taraf daalta raha .'' phir aapney usey phenk diya. rawahu Nasai ."
4406,"Hazrat Imam Malik bayan kartey hain, main napasand karta hun ki bachon ko soney ki koi chiz pahnaai jaey, kyonkey mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi pehenney se mana farmaya hai, so mein usey mardon ke liye pehanna napasand karta hun chaahey wo badey hon ya chhotey. ( rawahu Malik fil-Mauta ( ."
4407,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap aisey jootey pehantey they jin par baal nahin hotey they. Bukhari ."
4408,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke jooton ke do tasmey they. Bukhari ."
4409,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine eik ghazwa mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' jootey ka istemal ziyada tar karo, kyonkey aadmi jab jootey pehney huey hota hai to wo us waqt sawar hota hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4410,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi jootey pehney to wo daain se shuru karey aur jab utarey to pehley baayan utarey taake daayan paaon pehenney mein pehley ho aur utaarney mein aakhir par ho.'' muttafaq aleh."
4411,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs eik joota pehan kar na chaley phirey, wo dono jootey utaar kar chaley ya phir dono pehan kar chaley.'' muttafaq aleh."
4412,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke jootey ka tasma toot jaey to wo eik jootey mein na chaley yahan tak ke wo apna tasma marammat kar ley, eik mozey mein na chaley aur na baaeyn haath se khaye aur na eik kapdey mein got maar kar bethey aur na is tarah kapda lapetey ke uskey haath waghera bhi bahar na nikal saken.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4413,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke jooton ke do tasmey they aur dohrey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4414,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke koi shakhs joota khadey ho kar pehney. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4415,Hazrat Imam Tirmizi aur Imam ibne-Maja ne usey Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w ibne-Maja.
4416,"Hazrat Qasim bin Muhammad, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : kabhi-kabhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik jootey mein chaltey they. aur eik dusri riwayat mein hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) eik jootey mein chali thin. Tirmizi, aur farmaya : ye hadees ziyada sahih hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4417,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ye masnoon hai ke jab aadmi bethey to wo jootey utaar kar apni eik janib rakh ley. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4418,Hazrat ibn Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Najashi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein do siyah saada mozey bhejey to aapney unhen pehna. ibne-Maja aur Imam Tirmizi ne ibn Barida an abi ki sanad se ye izafa naqal kya hai : phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur un dono par masah kya. rawahu ibne-Maja w Tirmizi.
4419,"Hazrat Aaisha bayan karti hain, main haalate-haiz mein bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar mein kanghi kya karti thi. muttafaq aleh."
4420,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''paanch chizen fitrat se hain, khatna karna, zere-naf baal saaf karna, munchhein kutarna, nakhun taraashna aur baghlon ke baal udhadna.'' muttafaq aleh."
4421,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mushrikon ki mukhalifat karo, daadhiyan badhao aur munchhein katraao.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''moonchhein khub katraao aur daadhiyaan badhao.'' muttafaq aleh."
4422,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, munchhein katraaney, nakhun taraashney, baghlon ke baal ukhaadney aur zere-naaf baal moondney ke mutalliq hamarey liye waqt muqarrar kya gaya ke ham (unhen) chaalis roz se ziyada na choden. rawahu Muslim ."
4423,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''yahood w Nasara khizaab nahin lagatey, tum unke khilaf karo.'' muttafaq aleh."
4424,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Fateh Makka ke roz abu Qahaafa (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid Usman bin Aamir ( ko bulaya gaya to unka sar aur unki dadhi saghama (safed ghaas) ki tarah safed thi. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' uski safedi ko kisi doosrey rang mein tabdeel karo aur siyah rang se ijtinab karo.'' rawahu Muslim ."
4425,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jis mamley mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hukm na milta to aap is mein ehle-kitab se muwaafiqat karna pasand farmatey they. ehle-kitab apney baal sidhey chhodtey they jabkey mushrekin apney baalon ki mang nikala kartey they, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni peshani ke baal sidhey chodey, phir baad mein mang nikali. muttafaq aleh."
4426,"Hazrat Naafe, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ''qazaa'' se mana farmatey huey suna, Naafe se puchha gaya : ''qazaa'' kya hai? unhoney farmaya : bachey ke sar ke kuch hissey ko moond diya jaey aur kuch ko chhod diya jaey. Bukhari, Muslim . aur baaz muhaddeseen ne is tafseer ko hadees ke sath mila diya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4427,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik bacha dekha jiskey sar ka kuch hissey moond diya gaya tha aur kuch chhod diya gaya tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen us se mana kar diya aur farmaya : ''sara ( sar ( moondo ya sara chhod do.'' rawahu Muslim."
4428,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurton ke sath mushaabihat karney waley mardon aur mardon ke sath mushaabihat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaey. aur farmaya : ''unhen apney gharon se nikal do.'' Bukhari ."
4429,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne aurton se mushaabihat karney waley mardon aur mardon se mushaabihat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai.'' Bukhari."
4430,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baalon mein baal jodney wali aur baal judwaaney wali par aur badan godney wali aur gudwaaney wali par lanat farmaai. muttafaq aleh.
4431,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Allah Taala ne badan godney waaliyon aur badan gudwaaney waaliyon par, (chehrey aur palkon waghera ke) baal nochne waaliyon aur husn ki khatir daanton ko bareek w tez karney waaliyon par, Allah ki takhleeq ko badalney waaliyon par lanat farmaai. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas eik aurat aai to usney kaha : mujhey pata chala hai ke aapney aisi-aisi aurton par lanat ki hai? unhoney farmaya : mujhey kya hai ke jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat ki ho aur main is par lanat na karun? jabkey wo Allah ki kitab mein hai. us aurat ne kaha : maine pura Quran padha hai lekin jo aap kehtey hain, maine wo baat is mein nahin pai. unhoney farmaya : agar tum ne usey padha hota to tum ye baat is mein pa leti, kya tum ne ye nahin padha : ''Allah ke Rasool jo tumhen den usey ley lo aur jis se tumhen mana karen us se ruk jaao.'' usney kaha : kyon nahin, maine usey padha hai. unhoney farmaya : to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4432,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nazar ka lag jana Sabit hai, aur aapney badan godney se mana farmaya hai. Bukhari."
4433,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha dar-aan-haaleke aapney sar ke baalon ko chipkaya hua tha. Bukhari."
4434,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aadmi ke liye Zaafran ka istemal mamnoo qarar diya hai. muttafaq aleh."
4435,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, hamen jo behtareen khushbu muyassar hoti, wo mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko lagaya karti thi yahan tak ke main khushbu ki chamak aap ke sar aur aap ki dadhi mein paati thi. muttafaq aleh."
4436,"Hazrat Naafe bayan kartey hain, jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) b-khor (ki dhooni) letey to aap (kabhi) kaafur milaaey baghair b-khor wali lakdi ki dhuni letey they aur (kabhi) wo dhooni wali lakdi par kaafur bhi dal liya kartey they, phir farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) isi tarah dhooni liya kartey they. rawahu Muslim."
4437,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni munchhein katraatey they aur Ibrahim khaleelur-rehman bhi munchhein katraatey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4438,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apni munchhein nahin katraata wo ham mein se nahin.'' sahih rawahu Ahmed w Tirmizi w Nasai.
4439,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni dadhi ko tool w arz se tarashtey they. Tirmizi, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4440,"Hazrat Yala bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne is par khushbu ka asar dekha to farmaya : ''kya tumhari biwi hai?'' usney arz kya : nahin, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey dho dal, phir usey dho dal, phir usey dho dal, phir dobara na karna.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai."
4441,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah us shakhs ki, jiskey jism par khalooq ( khushbu ki eik qism) ka asar ho, Namaz qubul nahin karta .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4442,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main safar se apney ehle khana ke paas wapis aaya to merey haath phat gaey they, unhon ( ehle khana ( ne merey Zaafran ki khushbu laga di, mein subh ke waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap ko salam kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey salam ka jawab na diya aur farmaya : ''jaao aur usey apney ( badan ( se dho dalo .'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4443,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''murdon ki khushbu wo hai jiski khushbu ho magar rang na ho jabkey khawatin ki khushbu wo hai jis ka rang ho magar uski mehak na ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai ."
4444,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik murakkab qism ki khushbu thi jis se aap khushbu lagaya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4445,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar par bahut ziyada tel lagaya kartey they, apni dadhi mein khub kanghi kya kartey they, aur sar ko achi tarah dhanp kar rakha kartey they, goya aap ka kapda aisey tha jaisey teli ka kapda ho. ( rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah ( ."
4446,"Hazrat Umme-Hani (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, eik dafa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas Makka mein tashrif laye to aap ke chaar gesu they. rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood w Tirmizi w ibne-Maja."
4447,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sar ke baalon ki mang nikaalti to main aap ke taaloo se baalon ko alag karti aur aap ki peshani ke baalon ko aap ki aakhon ke darmiyan latka deti. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4448,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rozaana bila nagha kanghi karney se mana farmaya hai. rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
4449,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi ne Fazala bin Ubaid se kaha : kya wajeh hai ke main aap ke baal bikhrey huey dekhta hun? unhoney kaha, kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ziyada naaz se hamen mana kya kartey they, us shakhs ne kaha : kya wajeh hai ke main aap ko nangey paaon dekhta hun? unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamen hukm farmaya kartey they ke ham kabhi kabhar nangey paaon chala karen. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4450,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke baal hon wo unhen sanwaar kar rakhey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood .
4451,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safed baalon (budhapey) ko badalney wali sab se behtareen chiz mahndi aur wasma hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4452,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhiri zamaney mein kuch aisey log hongey jo us siyahi se kabootron ke seenon ki tarah khizaab karengey, wo jannat ki khushbu bhi nahin paeyngey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai."
4453,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sabti jootey (jin par baal nahin hotey they) pehna kartey they, aur waras (Yamen ke ilaqey ki eik buti) aur Zaafran se apni dadhi ko zard kya kartey they, aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aisey hi kya kartey they. rawahu Nasai."
4454,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik aadmi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra jisney mehndi lagai hui thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya khub hai ye! '' raawi bayan kartey hain, phir doosra aadmi guzra jisney mehndi aur wasma lagaya hua tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye us se bhi behtar hai.'' phir eik aur shakhs guzra jisney zard rang kya hua tha, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye un sab se behtar hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4455,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''budhapey (safed baalon) ko badal dalo aur yahood se mushaabihat na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4456,aur Imam Nasai ne usey ibne-Umar aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai . rawahu Nasai .
4457,aur Imam Nasai ne usey ibne-Umar aur ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya hai. rawahu Nasai . rawahu Nasai .
4458,"Hazrat Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se aur wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safed baal khatm na karo kyonkey wo musalman ka Noor hai, jiska haalate-Islam mein baal safed hota hai to uskey badley mein Allah uskey liye eik neki likh deta hai, uskey badle mein uski eik ghalati khatam kar deta hai aur uskey badle mein uska eik darja buland kar deta hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4459,Hazrat Kab bin Murra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ke haalat Islam mein baal safed hun to roze-qiyamat uskey liye Noor hoga.'' rawahu Tirmizi w Nasai.
4460,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik bartan mein ghusl kya kartey they, aap ke baal kandhon aur kanon ki lo ke darmiyan they. rawahu Tirmizi ."
4461,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi ibn Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Khurem achcha aadmi hai agar uskey baal lambey na hotey aur na wo apna tehband latkaata.'' Khurem ko ye baat pahunchi to usney ustara liya aur us se lambey baalon ko apney kanon tak kaat liya aur apna tehband apni nisf pindliyon tak utha liya . rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4462,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, meri peshani ke baal lambey they, meri walida ne mujhey kaha : main unhen nahin kaatungi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen khinchtey aur pakda kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4463,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aale-Jaafar ko teen roz tak haalate-gham mein rehney diya, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas tashrif laye to farmaya : ''aaj ke baad merey bhai par mat ronaa.'' phir farmaya : ''merey bhatijon ko bulao.'' hamen laya gaya goya ham choozey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hajjaam ko merey paas laao.'' aapney usey hukm farmaya to usney hamarey sar moond diye. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4464,"Hazrat umme-Atiya ansaariya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Madina main eik aurat khatney kya karti thi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : ''khatney ki jagah ziyada na kaato kyonkey wo aurat ke liye ziyada lazzat wala aur khawind ke liye ziyada pur lutf hai.'' Abu-Dawud, aur unhoney farmaya : ye hadees zaeef hai aur iskey raawi majhool hain. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4465,"Hazrat kareema bint Hammam se riwayat hai ke eik aurat ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se mehndi ke khizaab se mutalliq puchha to unhoney farmaya : koi muzaaeqa nahin, lekin main usey napasand karti hun, merey Habib ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( iski mehak ko napasand kya kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4466,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Hind bin Utba ne arz kya, Allah ke nabi! mujh se baiat lein, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tum se baiat nahin lunga yahan tak ke tum apni hatheliyon ka rang badlo, goya teri hatheliyan kisi darindey ki hatheliyan hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4467,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, eik aurat ne pardey ke peechey se ishara kya uskey haath mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke naam eik khat tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath khinch liya , aur farmaya : ''main nahin janta ke ye aadmi ka haath hai ya aurat ka haath hai? '' us aurat ne kaha : balke aurat ka haath hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum aurat hoti to tum mehndi ke sath apney naakhunon ka rang badalti.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood w Nasai ."
4468,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain bimari ke baghair baalon mein baal jodney wali aur judwaaney wali, baal nochne wali aur ukhadwaaney wali, badan godney wali aur gudwaaney wali par lanat ki gaee hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4469,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aurat ka sa libas pehanney waley mard aur mard ka sa libas pehanney wali aurat par lanat farmaai hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4470,"Hazrat ibne-abi Muleka (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se arz kya gaya, eik aurat (mardon jaisey) jootey pahanti hai (us ka kya hukm hai) unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mardon se mushaabihat karney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ."
4471,"Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) safar par jatey to aap apney ehle khana mein se Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se sab se aakhir par miltey aur jab aap safar se wapis tashrif latey to aap sab se pehley Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) se miltey. aap eik ghazwe se wapis tashrif laye to unhoney apney darwazey par parda latka rakha tha aur Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ko chaandi ke kangan pehna rakhey they, aap jab tashrif laye to Fatima (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein dakhil na huye, jis se unhoney samajh liya ke aap ke tashrif na laney ka sabab parda aur kangan hain, unhoney parda phaad dala aur bachchon ke haathon se kangan utaar diye aur unke tukdey kar diye , wo dono rotey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf chal diye , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un dono se wo kangan ley liye aur farmaya : ''Soban ! isey aale falan ke paas ley jaao , kyonkey ye merey ehal se hain, main napasand karta hun ke wo apni duniya ki zindagaani mein nafis chizen istimal karen, Soban ! Fatima ke liye asab (dariyaai janwer ke daant) ka haar aur haathi ke daant ke do kangan kharid laao.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood."
4472,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''asmad ka surma lagaya karo, kyonkey wo basaarat ko tezi bakhshta hai aur baal ugata hai.'' aur unka guman hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas surme-daani thi jis se aap her raat teen martaba is (aankh) mein aur teen martaba is (aankh) mein surma lagatey they. rawahu Tirmizi."
4473,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) her raat soney se pehley her aankh mein teen martaba As'fahaani surma lagaya kartey they, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''behtareen dawaai jiskey zariey tum ilaj kartey ho wo dawaai hai, jo munh ke andar eik janib mein dali jaey, aur wo dawaai jo naak ke zariey tapkai jaey aur pachhney lagwaanaa aur julab lena hai aur behtareen surma As'fahaani hai kyonkey wo basaarat ko tezi bakhshta hai aur (palkon ke) baal ugata hai, aur satarah, Unais aur ikkis taareekh ko pachhney lagwaanaa sab se behtar hai.'' aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Mairaj ke safar mein jis bhi jamaate malaaika ke paas se guzartey to unhoney yehi kaha : aap pachhney lagwaaney ko iltizaam (wajib) karen. Tirmizi, aur unhoney kaha : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi."
4474,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mardon aur aurton ko hamamon mein dakhil honey se mana farmaya , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mardon ko tehband pehan kar janey ki ijazat farmaee. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4475,"Hazrat Abu Maleeh bayan kartey hain, ehle-hims se kuchh aurten Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aayen. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : tum kahan se ho? unhoney bataya : mulk Sham sey, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : shayad ke tum kurah se ho jahan ki aurten hamamon mein jati hain? unhoney kaha : ji haan ! unhoney farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''aurat apney khawind ke ghar ke ilawa kisi jagah apney kapdey utarti hai to usney apney aur rab ke darmiyan haael hijaab chaak kar diya.'' eik dusri riwayat mein hai : ''apney ghar ke ilawa, to uskey aur Shan Wale Allah ke beech jo hijaab (parda) tha wo usney chaak kar diya.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4476,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumharey liye sarzameene ajam (ghair-arab) Fateh ho jaeygi aur tum wahan kuchh ghar paaogey jinhen Hammam kaha jaeyga, is mein sirf mard tehband baandh kar dakhil hon aur khawatin ko un mein janey se mana karo magar jo mareeza ho ya haalate-nifaas mein ho (usey ijazat hai).'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4477,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah aur yoame-aakhirat (aakhirat ke din) par eman rakhta hai wo tehband ke baghair Hammam mein na jaey aur jo shakhs Allah aur yoame aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo apni ehliya ko Hammam mein janey ki ijazat na dey aur jo shakhs Allah aur yoame aakhirat par eman rakhta hai wo aisey dasterkhaan par na bethey jahan sharab ka daur chalta ho.'' rawahu Tirmizi aur Nasai.
4478,"Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khizaab ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : agar main chahta ke aap ke sar ke safed baal shumar karun to main kar sakta tha, aur unhoney bayan kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khizaab nahin lagaya. eik dusri riwayat mein izafa naqal kiya : Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mahndi aur vasma ke sath khizaab kiya jabkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sirf mahndi se khizaab kiya. muttafaq aleh."
4479,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo apni dadhi ko zard rang diya kartey they yahan tak ke zard rang se unke kapdey bhar jatey they, un se puchha gaya, aap zard rang kyon lagatey hain? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko iskey sath rangtey huey dekha hai aur aap ko ye rang sab se ziyada pasand tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney tamam kapdey yahan tak ke apna amama bhi isi ke sath ranga kartey they. rawahu Abu-Dawood aur Nasai."
4480,"Hazrat Usman bin Abdullah bin Mohab bayan kartey hain, main Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaya to unhoney hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rangin baal dikhaye. Bukhari."
4481,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik mukhannas (hijdaa) laya gaya jisney apney haathon aur paaon par mahndi laga rakhi thi, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''iska kya maamla hai?'' unhoney arz kiya, wo aurton se mushaabihat karta hai, aapney uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya to usey naqeea' ki taraf jala watan kar diya gaya, aap se arz kiya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham usey qatl na kar den? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey namaaziyon ko qatl karney se mana kiya gaya hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4482,"Hazrat Waleed bin Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Makka Fateh kar liya to ehle-Makka apney bachchey aap ke paas laney lagey , aap unke liye barkat ki dua farmatey aur unke saron par haath phertey , mujhey bhi aap ki khidmat mein pesh kiya gaya jabkey maine khaluq (Zaafran ke sath makhloot (mili jhuli) khushbu) lagai hui thi, lihaza aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaluq ki wajeh se mujhey haath na lagaya. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4483,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se arz kiya, merey baal lambey (kandhon tak) hain, kya main un mein kanghi kar liya karun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan , aur inhen sanwaar kar rakh.'' raawi ne kaha, aur Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us qol ki wajeh se ke ''baalon ko sanwaar kar rakho.'' din mein do martaba baalon ko tel lagaya kartey they. rawahu Maalik."
4484,"Hazrat Hujjaj bin Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Anas bin Maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey, meri behan Mughira ne mujhey bataya ke tum un dino chhotey bachchey they aur tumhari do mendhiyan thin, unhoney tumharey sar par haath phera , barkat ki dua ki aur farmaya : in dono ko moond do ya inhen katar do kyonkey ye yahood ki zeenat aur aadat hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4485,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khawatin ko apney sar ke baal moondney se mana farmaya. rawahu Nasai."
4486,"Hazrat Ata bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein tashrif farma they ke eik aadmi aaya jiskey sar aur dadhi ke baal bikhre hue they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daste Mubarak se uski taraf ishara farmaya , goya aap usey apney baal aur dadhi sanwaarney ka hukm farma rahey hain, usney wesay hi kar liya aur phir wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye us se behtar hai ke tum mein se koi us haal mein aaye ke uskey sar ke baal bikhre hue hon goya wo shetan hai.'' rawahu Malik."
4487,"Hazrat ibne Musaiyeb se riwayat hai, unhen kehtey huey suna gaya ke ''Allah paak hai wo (apney bandon sey) safai aur khushbu pasand karta hai, wo paakiza hai nazaafat (paaki) ko pasand karta hai, wo karim hai karam ko pasand karta hai, wo sakhi data hai sakhawat karney ko pasand karta hai, mera khayal hai aapney farmaya : tum apney sahnon ko saaf suthra rakho, aur yahood ki naqal mat utaaro.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine muhajrin Mismaar se iska tazkira kiya to unhoney kaha : Aamir bin Saad ne usey apney walid ke wastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se isi tarah bayan kiya magar unhoney kaha : ''apney sehan saaf rakho.'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4488,"Hazrat Yahya bin Saeed se riwayat hai ke unhoney Saeed bin Musaiyeb ko bayan kartey huey suna, Ibrahim (Aleh.) Rehman ke Khaleel (dost) sab se pehley shakhs hain jinhon ne mehman nawaazi ki, unhoney sab se pehley khatna kiya, sab se pehley apni munchhein katrin, sab se pehley budhapa dekha to arz kiya, aey merey rab ! ye kya hai? rab tabarak w taala ne farmaya : Ibrahim ! waqar hai. arz kiya, aey merey rab ! merey waqar mein izafa farma. rawahu Malik."
4489,"Hazrat Abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ghar mein kuttey aur tasaaweer hon is mein (rehmat ke) farishtey dakhil nahin hotey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4490,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu), Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghamgin ho gaey aur farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) ne raat ke waqt mujh se mulaqat karney ka wada kiya tha lekin wo nahin aaye, aagah raho ke Allah ki qism ! usney mujh se kabhi wada khilafi nahin ki.'' phir aap ke dil mein khayal aaya ke aap ki chaarpai ke nichey kuttey ka chhota sa bachcha hai. aapney uskey mutalliq hukm farmaya : usey nikal diya jaey, chunanche usey nikal diya gaya, phir aapney haath mein pani lekar us jagah chhidak diya, phir jab Sham hui to Jibrael (Alaihissalam) aap se miley to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne kal mujh se mulaqat karney ka wada kiya tha?'' unhoney arz kiya : theek hai, lekin ham us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein kutta aur tasweer ho, agley roz subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kuttey maarney ka hukm farma diya yahan tak ke chhotey baaghon ke kuttey bhi maar diye jaeyn albatta badey baaghon ke kuttey chhod deney (yani na maarney) ka hukm farmaya. rawahu Muslim."
4491,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar mein aisi koi chiz nahin chhodtey they jis par tasweer hoti thi. Bukhari.
4492,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney eik chhota sa takiya kharid jis par taswiren thin, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey dekha to aap darwazey par khadey ho gaey aur andar tashrif na laye, maine aap ke chehrey par naa-pasandeedgi ke aasaar dekhey , wo bayan karti hain, maine arz kiya, Allah ke Rasool ! main (apni ghalati sey) Allah aur uskey Rasool ki taraf ruju karti hun, maine ghalati kya ki hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye takiya kaisa hai?''maine arz kiya, maine isey aap ke liye kharid hai ta ke aap is par tashrif farma hon aur is par tek lagaeyn, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''in tasweeron walon ko roze-qiyamat azab diya jaeyga, unhen kaha jaeyga, tum ne jo takhleeq kiya usey zinda karo.'' aur farmaya : ''be-shak wo ghar jis mein tasweer ho wahan farishtey dakhil nahin hotey.'' muttafaq aleh."
4493,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke unhoney ghar ke dareechey par parda latka rakha tha jis par taswiren thin, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey phaad dala , aur maine us se do takiye bana liye jo ke ghar mein they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un par betha kartey they. muttafaq aleh."
4494,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi ghazwe par tashrif ley gaey to maine eik kapda liya aur usey darwazey par latka diya, jab aap wapis tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wo kapda dekha to usey khinch kar phaad diya, phir farmaya : ''Allah taala ne hamein ye hukm nahin diya ke ham patthar aur mitti ko kapda pahnaaein.'' muttafaq aleh."
4495,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat karti hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat un logon ko sab se ziyada sakht azab diya jaeyga jo Allah ki takhleeq mein Allah se mushaabihat kartey hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4496,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah taala farmata hai is se badh kar kon zalim ho sakta hai jo meri tarah ki takhleeq karney lagta hai, unhen chahiye ke wo eik zarra ya eik dana ya eik jau to paida karen !'' muttafaq aleh."
4497,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ke yahan musawwiron (tasweer banane wale) ko sab se ziyada sakht azab diya jaeyga.'' muttafaq aleh."
4498,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''her musawwir aag mein (janey wala) hai, usney jo bhi tasweer banai hogi usey surat ata ki jaeygi aur wo us (musawwir) ko jahannam mein azab deygi.'' ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar tum ne zarur hi tasweer Banani hai to phir darkht aur aisi chiz ki bina jis mein rooh na ho. muttafaq aleh."
4499,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs kisi aisey khuwab dekhney ka dawa karey jo usney dekha nahin to usey mukallaf banaya jaeyga ke wo do jo ke darmiyan gireh lagaey aur wo hergiz aisa nahin kar sakega , jo shakhs kaan laga kar logon ki baaten sunta hai jabkey wo usey napasand kartey hon ya wo us se door bhagtey hon to roze-qiyamat uskey kanon mein seesa dala jaeyga aur jisney koi tasweer banai usey azab diya jaeyga aur usey mukallaf banaya jaeyga ke wo is mein rooh phoonkey aur wo aisa nahin kar sakega.'' Bukhari."
4500,Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs nard (shatraj) khelta hai to wo aisey hai jaisey usney khinzir ke gosht aur uskey khoon se apna haath rangin kiya ho.'' rawahu Muslim.
4501,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael (Alaihissalam) merey paas aaye to unhoney kaha : main guzishta raat aap ke paas aaya tha lekin aap ke darwazey par moortiyaan thin jin ki wajeh se main andar nahin aaya, aur ghar main eik parda tha jis par moortiyaan thin aur ghar main eik kutta bhi tha, ghar ke darwazey par jo moortiyaan hain unke sar qaat deney ka hukm farmaain to wo darkht ki tarah ho jaeygi, aur pardey ke mutalliq hukm farmaain ke usey kaat kar do takiye bana len jo phenkey aur raundey jaeyn jabkey kuttey ke mutalliq hukm farmaain ke usey bahar nikal diya jaey.'' isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisa hi kiya. rawahu Tirmizi aur Abu-Dawood."
4502,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat jahannam ki aag se eik gardan nikleygi jiski do aankhen dekhney wali hongi, do kaan sunney waley hongey aur eik zaban bolti hogi , wo kaheygi : mujhey teen qism ke logon, her zalim aur mutakabbir shakhs, Allah ke sath kisi aur ko mabud bananey waley aur tasweer bananey walon, par maamoor kiya gaya hai (ke main unhen aag mein dakhil karun).'' rawahu Tirmizi."
4503,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''be-shak Allah Taala ne sharab, jooey aur tabley ko haram qarar diya hai.'' aur farmaya : ''her nasha-aawar chiz haram hai.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4504,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sharab, juey, tabal aur ''ghubaira'' se mana farmaya hai, aur ''Ghubira'' sharab hai jisey Habshi makai se banaya kartey they, aur usey skurka bhi kaha jata hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood."
4505,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne nardsheer (shatranj) kheli usney Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani ki.'' rawahu Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood.
4506,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko eik kabootri ka peechha kartey huey dekha to farmaya : ''shetan, shaitaana ka peechha kar raha hai.'' (rawahu Ahmed, Abu-Dawood, ibne-Maja aur al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4507,"Hazrat Saeed bin Abul Hasan bayan kartey hain, main ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha jab eik aadmi unke paas aaya, usney kaha : ibne-Abbas ! main eik aisa aadmi hun ke meri maeeshat (rozi-roti) ka inhisaar (nirbhar) dast kaari par hai, aur main ye tasaaweer banata hun, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suni hui hadees hi suna deta hun, maine aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jis shakhs ne koi tasweer banai to Allah usey azab deta rahega yahan tak ke wo is mein rooh phoonkey jabkey wo kabhi bhi is mein rooh nahin phunk sakega.'' us aadmi ne bada saans liya aur uska chehra zard pad gaya is par Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : afsos tujh par, agar tum ne zarur yehi kaam karna hai to phir darkht aur aisi chizon ki tasaaweer bana liya kar jis mein rooh na ho.'' Bukhari."
4508,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bimar huey to aap ki eik biwi ne Kaneesa ka zikr kiya jisey Maariya kaha jata hai, Umme-Salma aur Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) sarzameene-habsha gaee thin, unhoney uskey Husan aur is mein rakhi hui tasaaweer ka zikr kiya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar uthaya aur farmaya : ''ye wo log hain ke jab un mein Saleh aadmi faut ho jata to wo uski qabr par masjid bana letey, phir us (masjid) mein ye taswiren bana detey, ye Allah ki bad-tareen makhluq hain.'' muttafaq aleh."
4509,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''roze-qiyamat aisey shakhs ko sab se sakht azab hoga jisney kisi Nabi ko qatl kiya ya kisi Nabi ne usey qatl kiya, ya kisi ne apney waliden mein se kisi eik ko qatl kiya, isi ke saath musawwir (chitrakar) aur aisa aalim jisney apney ilm se (amal ke zariey) faeyda hasil na kiya. '' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan)."
4510,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo kaha kartey they : shatranj ajmiyon ka jua hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4511,Hazrat ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai ke Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : khatakar shakhs hi shatranj khelta hai. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4512,Hazrat ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai ke un se shatranj khelney ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : wo batil khelon mein se hai jabkey Allah Taala batil ko pasand nahin karta. ye chaaron ahadis Imam Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein riwayat ki hain. ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( .
4513,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ansaar ke eik ghar mein tashrif laya kartey they, jabkey unke qarib eik ghar tha (aap unke yahan nahin jaya kartey they ( un par ye shaaq guzra to unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap falan ke ghar tashrif latey hain aur hamarey ghar tashrif nahin latey , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kyonkey tumharey ghar mein kutta hai.'' unhoney arz kya : aur unke ghar mein bula hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bula darinda hai.'' rawahu daar-qutni."
